<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Samirs | Cloud & DevOps Solutions</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
background:#f5f7fb;
color:#333;
}

header{
background:#0b3d91;
color:white;
padding:20px 0;
}

.container{
width:90%;
max-width:1100px;
margin:auto;
}

nav{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
}

nav h1{
margin:0;
}

nav ul{
list-style:none;
display:flex;
gap:20px;
padding:0;
margin:0;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
background:linear-gradient(120deg,#0b3d91,#1f77ff);
color:white;
padding:80px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.hero h2{
font-size:40px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:18px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
background:white;
color:#0b3d91;
padding:12px 25px;
border-radius:5px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

.section{
padding:60px 20px;
}

.section h2{
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.features{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:30px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:30px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
text-align:center;
}

.card h3{
margin-bottom:15px;
color:#0b3d91;
}

.cta{
background:#0b3d91;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:60px 20px;
}

footer{
background:#222;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="container">
<nav>
<h1>Samirs</h1>
<ul>
<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Solutions</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
</ul>
</nav>
</div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h2>Cloud, DevOps & AI Solutions</h2>
<p>Helping businesses build scalable, secure, and modern cloud platforms.</p>
<a class="btn" href="#">Get Started</a>
</section>

<section class="section">
<h2>Our Services</h2>

<div class="features">

<div class="card">
<h3>Cloud Architecture</h3>
<p>Design scalable infrastructure on AWS, Azure and GCP for modern applications.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>DevOps Automation</h3>
<p>CI/CD pipelines, containerization, Kubernetes and infrastructure automation.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Security & DevSecOps</h3>
<p>Application security scanning, compliance automation and runtime protection.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>AI Platforms</h3>
<p>Build intelligent applications using modern AI frameworks and cloud services.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="cta">
<h2>Ready to transform your business?</h2>
<p>Let us help you modernize your infrastructure and accelerate innovation.</p>
<a class="btn" href="#">Contact Us</a>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 samirs.co.in | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
